crack                   Parse R Markdown or R scripts
engines                 Language engines
fuse                    Render Markdown, R Markdown, and R scripts
fuse_book               Fuse multiple R Markdown documents to a single
                        output file
fuse_env                The 'fuse()' environment
fuse_site               Fuse R Markdown documents individually under a
                        directory
get_context             Get the 'fuse()' context
html_format             Output formats in YAML metadata
litedown-package        A lightweight version of R Markdown
markdown_options        Markdown rendering options
pkg_desc                Print the package description, news, citation,
                        manual pages, and source code
raw_text                Mark a character vector as raw output
reactor                 Get and set chunk options
roam                    Preview Markdown and R Markdown files
timing_data             Get the timing data of code chunks and text
                        blocks in a document
vest                    Add CSS/JS assets to HTML output
